---
title: Goat's Cheese Burgers with sweet chilli drizzle and potato wedges
description: These succulent goat's cheese burgers are super simple to assemble but when it comes to flavour, they really pack a punch. Added tastiness comes in the form of the sweet chilli drizzle, juicy tomato, and mouth-watering potato wedges.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W02_IE_IEXCFB0123-7_MAIN_high-9cfa1612.jpeg
